fr:mainmatter.fr:p:
Let C\xrightarrow {F} D be a functor with C small and D
complete. Then there is an equalizer diagram





    \usepackage{tikz, tikz-cd, mathtools, amssymb}
  \usetikzlibrary{shapes.geometric}
