    C\ar [rr, "F", ""'{name=F}]\ar [dr, "K"'] && E\\
    & D\ar [ur, "\operatorname *{Ran}_K F"']\ar [to=F, Rightarrow, "\epsilon "']
  \end {tikzcd}


 with E locally small is pointwise if it is is
preserved by all covariant hom-functors. Dually, a left
Kan extension is pointwise if the dual data 




