  \end {tikzcd}


 is preserved by all contravariant hom-functors.

Explicitly, a left Kan extension consists of a functor D\xrightarrow {\operatorname *{Lan}_K} F together with a
  natural transformation F\xrightarrow {\eta } (\operatorname *{Lan}_K F)K, as in 




